'''WYCIWYG''' is an [[acronym]] for <i>'''W'''hat '''Y'''ou '''C'''ache '''I'''s '''W'''hat '''Y'''ou '''G'''et</i>. A [[Uniform Resource Identifier|URI]] scheme specific to the [[Mozilla]] family of [[web browsers]] which indicates that a link should be preferentially fetched from [[cache]] instead of from the web [[Server (computing)|server]].

Abbreviation derived from, but unrelated to, [[WYSIWYG]].


